==Description==

The '''TechDraw ExtensionHoleCircle''' tool adds centerlines to a circular pattern of circles.

[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionHoleCircleExample.png|400px]]
{{Caption|On the right a circular pattern with centerlines}}

==Usage==

# Optionally specify the line attributes with the [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes|TechDraw ExtensionSelectLineAttributes]] tool.
# Select three or more circles forming a circular pattern.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionHoleCircle.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionHoleCircle|Add Bolt Circle Centerlines]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Extensions: Centerlines/Threading → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionHoleCircle.svg|16px]] Add Bolt Circle Centerlines}} option from the menu.
# The centerlines are added.


